{"tid":1761984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫助同路人 防止混水摸魚 使用黃色眾籌認証機制","createTime":"2019-11-29T09:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T11:52:58.000Z","uid":30791,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"457e79234ff73b5a53dd19dbb3c981f97bd727d7","tid":1761984,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:07:44.000Z","msg":"為左防止混水摸魚 又幫到有需要既人 可以考慮以下機制去做眾籌<br />\n<br />\n1. 受助者尋找可靠既黃絲/議員/KOL/機構 (代理人) 向佢講自己既情況 需要多少金錢資助<br />\n2. 代理人 Fact Check<br />\n3. 發起眾籌<br />\n4. 捐助者可以向 代理人 查証"},{"pid":"d7d7cfcff57a79650eaff0269ceccb8742c2be8a","tid":1761984,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a3390f7ac11c47fc5d67169ce7e7a06c34d90c","tid":1761984,"uid":214173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"關鍵係第二點,代理人唔易做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6b1e70731ea27b1218f33f871d00e129973eed","tid":1761984,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99a3390f7ac11c47fc5d67169ce7e7a06c34d90c","tid":1761984,"uid":214173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"關鍵係第二點,代理人唔易做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:12:44.000Z","msg":"推到星火搞番一個代理人機構 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3287a218438e8e4984b0972e64d99107ede9d47","tid":1761984,"uid":30791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"99a3390f7ac11c47fc5d67169ce7e7a06c34d90c","tid":1761984,"uid":214173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"關鍵係第二點,代理人唔易做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:17:43.000Z","msg":"最簡單既認証包括：<br />\n口供紙<br />\n拘捕通知<br />\n入院紙<br />\n收入証明<br />\n身份証<br />